Package com.mumfrey.liteloader.transformers

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Callback
    Target information for injected callback methods
    CallbackInjectionTransformer
    Transformer which injects callbacks by searching for profiler invokations and RETURN opcodes
    ClassOverlayTransformer
    This transformer applies one class to another as an "overlay".
    ClassTransformer
    Base class for transformers which work via ClassNode
    PacketTransformer Deprecated
    This transformer will be retired in favour of event-based packed hooks for 1.8 and beyond
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Callback.CallbackType
    Type of callback to inject
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    InvalidOverlayException  
    PacketHandlerException
    Exception which a packet handler can throw in order to cancel further handling of the event
  • Error Summary 
    Error Description
    InjectedCallbackCollisionError  
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    AppendInsns
    Annotation which instructs the ClassOverlayTransformer to append instructions from the annotated method to the target method.
    Obfuscated
    Annotation which provides the obfuscated names for a method or field to the ClassOverlayTransformer
    Stub
    Interface which instructs the ClassOverlayTransformer to NOT merge the annotated method
